latestIgtvVideos.title: #fussyisfantastic
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Are you a fussy mom?
While I am actually a big fussy and an orthodox mom considering things around my kids be it home made food or screen watch. I can say 'No' infinity times when it comes to my kids safety for that whatever people call me🙆‍♀️
. 
Recently I have watched @kareenakapoor in a video being a fussy mom too. Truly felt so good that I am not alone🤪
. 
Thanks @firstcryindia for making me more confident #fussyisfantastic for being fussy in things that doesn't go according to others🤪. 
.
In collaboration with @firstcryindia, When I first saw the film I felt everymom should watch it for sure to put their guilt if any out their heart🤗. 
Hope mommies #belikeafussymom would love to watch the wonderful video put up by @firstcryindia for spreading #fussyisfantastic idea more.
.
